DOCKER:

docker ps
docker ps --all
docker run <image name>
docert stop <container id/name>
docker start < container id/name>
docker exec -it <container name> <cmd>
docker run -d <image name>
docker build -t <name> .
docker push <accountName/imagename>
docker kill <container id/name>
docker rm <container id/name> - remove containers
docker rmi <image name> = remove images
docker pull <image name>
docker run -p 80:5000 webapp

Map a volume on your local disk to volume on a docker container:
docker run -v /opt/datadir:/var/lib/mysql <mysql>

Details on a container:
docker inspect <container id/name>

Logs:
docker logs <container id/name>
